attributes.name: Urb - 2.7g AIO - Strawberry Shortcake
attributes.body:
Welcome New Mexico’s largest disposable vape to hit the market, 2.7 grams of premium vaping. With 3 variable voltage settings and preheat function, each consumer can dial in their perfect puff.


Strawberry Shortcake, this indica strain is a result of crossing the famous Juliet and Strawberry Diesel strains, resulting in a unique and captivating cannabis experience. Your taste buds are greeted with a burst of sweet strawberries, accompanied by hints of creamy undertones. This harmonious blend of fruity and dessert-like flavors makes it a true palate pleaser.


THC 90-97%

CBD 69.53-78.70%
